details.agePolicy:
Senior tickets are valid for adults 60+.
Child tickets for 2 - 12 years.
Student: Age 13+ with valid student ID.
Not all ticket types are available for all performances.
Rated-R Films: Under 17 requires accompanying parent or adult guardian (age 21 or older).  25 years and under must show ID for rated R movies.

Distraction-Free Entertainment

In an effort to provide the most enjoyable experience for
adults attending R-rated features in the evenings, no
children younger than 6 will be admitted to these
features after 6 p.m

offer.termsAndConditions: Purchase must be made between 9:00 a.m. PT on 7/10/2018 and 9:00 a.m. PT on 7/17/2018 for tickets to  ‘Skyscraper’, using a Fandango VIP account. At least some of the purchase must be paid using a credit or debit card, PayPal, credit in your Fandango VIP account from a prior exchanged purchase, or a Fandango (or Fandango-eligible theater) gift card.  Tickets must be for movie with showtime starting before 11:59 p.m. PT August 31, 2018.  You will not receive VIP+ points if you refund or exchange the ticket, and VIP+ points will post to your account about 24 hours after you see the movie in the theater.  When you receive 600 VIP+ Points, you will receive a $6 Discount Reward which you will need to convert into a Discount Promo Code for use on a qualifying purchase on Fandango, FandangoNOW or Fandango FanShop.  Discount Promo Code expires 14 days after Discount Reward is posted to your Fandango VIP account. Discount Promo Code cannot be combined with any other offer, promo code or discount, and cannot be used to purchase a gift card or toward shipping and handling.  Any unused balance will automatically expire.  Fandango may modify or cancel this offer at any time and without notice. This offer is subject to the VIP+ Program Terms at https://www.fandango.com/policies/vip-plus-program-terms and Fandango’s Terms and Policies and Privacy Policy at www.fandango.com/Terms-and-Policies.
